snippet.title: Feudal Lands: Alpha Coming March 2024
snippet.description:
Visit feudallands.com for more info or to pre-order now! 

Alpha keys available for a limited time. Follow us on twitter @playfeudallands. 

Join our discord: https://www.feudallands.com. We are kind of quiet and working, but we do answer questions ;). 

See you soon in Solstice!
